{"tid":516961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元旦金門同時掛中華民國國旗和中華人民共和國五星國旗　黃安樂喊：統一更近了","createTime":"2018-01-02T00:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T01:39:31.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a53804f5b7c6c0e71b61a62a21fcfeb72ea44434","tid":516961,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T00:14:41.000Z","msg":"金門同時掛國旗和五星旗　黃安樂喊：統一更近了<br />\n<br />\n金門模範街今天元旦不僅掛上了青天白日滿地紅國旗，甚至還掛上了中國五星旗，成為「<br />\n一邊一國」、「兩岸一家親」的特殊情況，藝人黃安也藉題發揮，表示「太棒了！統一，<br />\n是大勢所趨。」<br />\n<br />\n黃安今天在《微博》發文表示，自己曾經在金門當兵，金門曾經是最前線，今天卻同時掛<br />\n了五星旗和青天白日滿地紅旗，一片喜洋洋的氣氛，顯見統一是中華兒女共同心願，「金<br />\n門，我給你點讚！2018，距離統一更近了！」<br />\n（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180101/640_3da1adf4676bb80abd4ea85bcfca54d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180101%2F640_3da1adf4676bb80abd4ea85bcfca54d4.jpg&h=e74ca706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/k3wG1V\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fk3wG1V&d=JKeqFOzvXgpWegoe5nCsub%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2f055581\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/k3wG1V</a>"},{"pid":"ecf92ed92b3501fd9701b60ff44831a430f09257","tid":516961,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T00:16:14.000Z","msg":"中華民國唯一領土金馬快被統一了"},{"pid":"5cf6a4e8e665e6cebf4a727412d63b6bf66d7cfd","tid":516961,"uid":99225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T00:17:12.000Z","msg":"金門可以好快同中國統一<br />\n不過台灣唔會"},{"pid":"91afe35d7c1415b807decc97c9e95330cffc7bfb","tid":516961,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T00:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金門可以好快同中國統一<br />\n不過台灣唔會</blockquote><br />\n金馬係中國領土<br />\n屬於福建省"},{"pid":"baaa72e5bb912f1cd23de7c152f61c9e808fd4d1","tid":516961,"uid":20227,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T00:19:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid"